text: Diana Reyes (born November 18, 1979) is a Mexican singer. She records duranguense music. She was born in La Paz, Baja California Sur. She has released three gold records since 2004: La Reina del Pasito Duranguense, Las No. 1 de la Reina, and Te Voy a Mostrar. ==References== Category:Mexican singers Category:Latin singers Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:People from Baja California Sur
